# StateError.watchNotPaired

**Case**

The current device doesn’t have a paired Apple Watch.

## Declaration

```swift
case watchNotPaired
```

## Getting the error type

- **StateError.workoutApplicationNotInstalled**: The Workout app isn’t installed on this Apple Watch.
